scene.message:
Nanjo: He can't even make{nl}
proper use of a petty post{nl}
like student council pres.{nl}
Truly a small man.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I dunno, that student{nl}
council pres bugs me...{waitkey}Ahhh, I just wanna{nl}
go to the pa...{wait_fr:64}{nl}
I mean, the hospital!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Honestly, any of the{nl}
council officers would make{nl}
a better pres than him.{waitkey}{ret}

Student Council Pres: Sorting{nl}
through old records isn't a{nl}
student council pres's job!{waitkey}{clearbox}Senpai Kamitori would've{nl}
refused this on principle...{waitkey}{clearbox}Right — to follow in his{nl}
footsteps, I refuse too!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Student Council Pres.{nl}
Head of the St. Hermelin{nl}
student council.{nl}
Apparently not very diligent.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Council Officer: Our pres just{nl}
gives orders and does nothing{nl}
himself. Who voted for him?{waitkey}{clearbox}If I were pres, I'd work{nl}
that guy to the bone!{waitkey}{ret}

Council Officer: He's really{nl}
something, that guy — somehow{nl}
teachers love him anyway...{waitkey}{clearbox}He's never once been{nl}
lectured. Life really{nl}
isn't fair!{waitkey}{ret}

Council Officer: Our pres{nl}
wants to be like Kamitori,{nl}
the 18th council pres.{waitkey}{clearbox}You don't know him?{nl}
He's an alumnus who became{nl}
branch director at Sebek{waitkey}{nl}
at a young age. Quite{nl}
the impressive guy.{waitkey}{ret}
